{"tid":1790570,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"市民參與 Parkour 練習被指藏有木棍　警拘 6 青年","createTime":"2019-12-20T06:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T04:48:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":178,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce173753ed05ee4f3194bbbd8add63ecab292a9","tid":1790570,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"【11:40 更新報道，新增警方回覆】<br />\n<br />\n市民集合強身健體，但有可能引來警察干預。九龍城愛民選區候任區議員麥瑞淇昨日在 Facebook 專頁表示，有 6 名身穿黑衫的市民，前日（12 月 18 日）傍晚到何文田愛民邨參與「飛躍道訓練」，但是被防暴警員拘捕。警方指，約 10 名市民在場揮動木棍，警方接報後到場，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器拘捕 6 人。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》引述麥瑞淇說，被捕的 6 名人士，較活動原定時間早逾半小時到場，不久後就被防暴警察到場截查，帶上警車離開。<br />\n<br />\n麥瑞淇也在 Facebook 表示，負責導師亦只有其中一位被捕人士的資料。6 名被捕人士當中，5 人獲星火同盟的律師跟進。<br />\n<br />\n而根據「香港飛躍道協會」在 12 月 13 日的帖文，他們安排了在 12 月 18 日在愛民邨安排免費練習，練習時間 7 時半至 9 時半，練習重點包括「保護人上落」、「跑」、「跳」和「爬」。協會表示，他們未有限制參與人數，亦不需要事先報名參加。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆《立場新聞》說，在 18 日下午 6 時許，接獲一名男子報案，約 10 人在愛民邨一平台聚集及揮動木棍，警員接報後到場，在 6 名男子身上檢獲 6 支木棍，經初步調查後，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器罪名，拘捕 6 名年齡屆乎 22 至 34 歲本地男子。案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。被捕人士現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20191220-09_uBr9d_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20191220-09_uBr9d_1200x0.png&h=8bbe4d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-parkour-%E7%B7%B4%E7%BF%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%A8%E6%A3%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98-6-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587-parkour-%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598-6-%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=be9ae905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587-parkour-%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%25A8%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598-6-%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&h=9a9787de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87-parkour-%E7%B7%B4%E7%BF%92%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%A8%E6%A3%8D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98-6-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4/</a>"},{"pid":"cc1a5b185211d6a31ca915fe8741ee272164f3d6","tid":1790570,"uid":12864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeadcbe76cf780a869e28de046fcf08d1f8fb7d","tid":1790570,"uid":70786,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff16a5bcad68d7d1627a90eabe794d11ee0e568a","tid":1790570,"uid":57217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"406825f8af51b543894844629ac731273be62ca9","tid":1790570,"uid":3457,"like":28,"dislike":13,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"唔好拎木棍 下次拎藤條 睇你點拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347b77cdd693ce8af0ffe734f323a519b43daed5","tid":1790570,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"正呀"},{"pid":"cbcd72afa0251847770e61dc783d50275dc2736e","tid":1790570,"uid":21920,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:07:54.000Z","msg